{"tid":1424864,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個黑警心目中唔係攻擊性武器既物件","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:00:00.000Z","uid":41487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a2e92eb525959a04ebf52ba2973bfad83ce541b3","tid":1424864,"uid":41487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:41:16.000Z","msg":"我先，鐵通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a48c1022fdbc961055e11fd4448adca6d631f6","tid":1424864,"uid":41487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"我諗唔到喇"},{"pid":"43b3395e767d732a990f122cb71aaae02f1aa857","tid":1424864,"uid":118647,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"佢老母個閪，任人屌"},{"pid":"890cd77dba0f7404f90654a040d4789f573c187d","tid":1424864,"uid":210037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:44:30.000Z","msg":"唔需要任何物品，胸部都可以襲警，而且成功入罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下「荒謬」情況，應該唔會出現：<br />\n清潔工拒絕倒垃圾 - 掃把可以成為攻擊性武器<br />\n超級市場、家品店拒絕售賣貨品 - 售賣食品、家居物品可以成為攻擊性武器<br />\n老師拒絕教書 - 教學器材 (如粉筆、 pointer ) 可以成為攻擊性武器<br />\n書店拒絕賣書、圖書館闗閉 - 字典可以成為攻擊性武器<br />\n花店拒絕賣花 - 植物的尖剌可以成為攻擊性武器<br />\n餐廳關閉 - 玻璃器皿、鐵器可以成為攻擊性武器<br />\n仲有好多例子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e15525bf9f9a93cff0ead0f099866da58b080a","tid":1424864,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:44:36.000Z","msg":"愛貓入 聽日6點 各自去鴨記買laser比貓玩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1424549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1424549</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65ee4abedcbcf5518be64ba1598c2bdb73d872a3","tid":1424864,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"